channel.title: Help with Moparscape Server Status List
channel.description: Well, I recently got my no-ip up and working. But when I went to submit my server, it continues to say that it's offline. I can use the no-ip address for myself, but apparently others can't. I'm thinking it's something wrong with my computer, not no-ip. I tried turning off my firewall, and it still didn't help. And yes, I have port forwarded.
